@@TJvTrayIcon.Active
Description:
if active is true, the icon will be visible in the tray icon.

================================================================
@@TJvTrayIcon.Animated
Description:
Set this property to tree if you want to use the ICons. The component will change the icon every X seconds (specified in Delay).

================================================================
@@TJvTrayIcon.ApplicationVisible
Description:
if this property is false, your Application won't be visible in the bar... So, if you want to hide your Application and to put the icon in the tray bar, put this property to false and put Active to true. (don't forget to hide your forms too)

================================================================
@@TJvTrayIcon.Delay
Description:
This is the delay before to change the icon if animated is true.

