================================================================
@@TJvTrayIcon.OnMouseDown
Description:
This event is called when the user double click with the left button on the icon

================================================================
@@TJvTrayIcon.OnMouseMove
Description:
This event is called when the mouse move over the icon

================================================================
@@TJvTrayIcon.OnMouseUp
Description:
This event is called when the button of the mouse goes up over the icon

================================================================
@@TJvTrayIcon.PopupMenu
Description:
This is the PopupMenu you want to see when the user right click your icon

================================================================
@@TJvTrayIcon.VisibleInTaskList
Description:
This property enables you to hide your Application from the task list (what you see when you press ctrl+alt+del). This may not be available in all oses.

